Cơ kiến. Vision according to the natural capacity, seeing the Buddha according to natural endowment.

Cơ ứng. Potentiality and response, Xem cơ cảm.

Cờ. Patàkà, Dhvaja, Ketu (S). Flag, banner. Also phướn, tràng phan.

